request.description:
This endpoint is use for product creeation.


## Payload
`name`: `required` product name

`min_amount`: `required` minimium amount for the product

`max_amount`: `required` maximium amount for the product

`inerest_rate`: `required` interest rate for the product

`product_type_id`: `required` id of the product type

`repayment_method_id`: `required` repayment method

`repayment_model_id`: `required` reapayment model. required for a loan product.

`tenor_types`: `required` array of object id representing tenor id

`is_fixed`: `optional` Default to 0 for saving product. Not required for loan product

`withholding_tax_rate`: `optional` Set withholding tax for a fixed saving plan, defaults to 0

`penal_charge_rate`: `optional` amount to charge if withdrawal is made before the maturity date`

request.description:
This endpoint is use for product creeation.


## Payload
`name`: `required` product name

`min_amount`: `required` minimium amount for the product

`max_amount`: `required` maximium amount for the product

`inerest_rate`: `required` interest rate for the product

`product_type_id`: `required` id of the product type

`repayment_method_id`: `required` repayment method

`repayment_model_id`: `required` reapayment model. required for a loan product.

`tenor_types`: `required` array of object id representing tenor id

`is_fixed`: `optional` Default to 0 for saving product. Not required for loan product

`withholding_tax_rate`: `optional` Set withholding tax for a fixed saving plan, defaults to 0

`penal_charge_rate`: `optional` amount to charge if withdrawal is made before the maturity date`
Get product by product id

request.description: deletes a whitelist

This is used for creating fees for a loan products.
Use `meta/codes?code_description={{code_description}}` to get ids of fee type, category and applicable_to


## Payload

`name`: `required` The name of the fee to create

`category_id`: `required` The category of fee could be `Regular` or `penal`

`type_id`: `required` The type of fee, could be `fixed`, `percentage` or `hybrid`

`applicable_to_id`: `required` What the fee is applicable_to `principal` or `principal + interest`

`percentage`: The percentage to charge. `required` if `type` is `Percentage` 

`min_amount`: The minimum amount to charge. `required` if `type` is `Percentage` or `Hybrid` 

`max_amount`: The maximum amount to charge. `required` if `type` is `Percentage` or `Hybrid` 

`frequency`: `optional` The frequency of the charge, applicable to penal charged. 


## Constraint

`min_amount` or `max_amount` must be specified if the `type` is `Hybrid` or `Percentage`
